        "CargoGradeToken": [
            "Medium"
        ],
        "Contractor|HaulCargo_AtoB": [
            "Hello,\n\nNeed a contractor for a simple cargo haul going from a freight elevator at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> to a freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>. At most the containers will be <EM4>8 SCU</EM4> in size. \n\nAlso, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along. \n\nAny chance you\u2019re available to take care of it for us?\n\nCovalex Independent Contractors\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
            "Hi,\n\nA freight elevator at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> has some cargo that needs to be delivered to a freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>. Another hauler backed out at the last minute because their ship couldn't handle <EM4>8 SCU containers</EM4>, so you\u2019d be doing me a big favor if you could take care of it.\n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\nCovalex Independent Contractors\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
            "Hi,\n\nA new haul just popped up. Details are below, if you\u2019re interested.\n\n1. Pick up cargo from a freight elevator at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>. Max size will be <EM4>8 SCU</EM4>. \n2. Deliver to a freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>. \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.    \n\nCovalex Independent Contractors\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered."
        ],
